<DATELINE>
<P>
BAGHDAD, Iraq 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The government of Iraq, seeking to rehabilitate the reputation of its monarchy 
30 years after overthrowing the last king, Sunday ordered that graves be built 
for its ancient rulers. 
</P>
